  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl58_LabelType\">You&rsquo;ve told too many lies, and made up too many cover stories, and now even you can&rsquo;t keep it all straight. The lies have become reality to you, which makes it difficult to think of a new convincing lie. You hesitate at crucial moments when trying to fool those around you, and likely shouldn&rsquo;t be in the field at all anymore.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Effects</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl58_LabelType\">You take a -2 penalty on Bluff checks and saving throws against illusions.</span></p>",
